───────────────────────────────────────────
Section 7  Termination
───────────────────────────────────────────

  1. If you violate any term of this License, all rights granted to you
     hereunder terminate automatically and immediately, without notice from
     the Copyright Holder.

  2. Upon termination, you must immediately cease all use, copying, and
     distribution of the Software and any Derivative Works.

  3. If you cure the violation in full within thirty (30) days of receiving
     notice of the violation from the Copyright Holder, and it is your first
     violation, your rights are automatically reinstated. Subsequent violations
     are not eligible for automatic reinstatement and require the Copyright
     Holder's written consent.

  4. Termination does not affect the rights of third parties who have
     lawfully received copies of the Software under this License prior to
     termination.

