Section 9  Governing Law and Dispute Resolution
───────────────────────────────────────────

This License is governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the
jurisdiction in which the Copyright Holder is domiciled. Any dispute arising
out of or relating to this License shall first be submitted to good-faith
negotiation between the parties. If negotiation fails, the dispute shall be
submitted to a court of competent jurisdiction in the Copyright Holder's
